Package serverSide.sharedRegions

Class GeneralRepos

  • java.lang.Object
    • serverSide.sharedRegions.GeneralRepos
  • public class GeneralRepos
extends java.lang.Object
    General Repository for the program. Implements the LoggerInterface interface, with a logger that writes the logs to a file. Also has the intervening entities and the shared regions needed to print the logs.
    Author:
    Martim Neves, Tiago Dias
